00:01:25,543 --> 00:01:30,215
Reka Soma, Francuska
I. Svetski Rat

3
00:01:57,242 --> 00:01:58,702
Gospodine? Gde ste krenuli?

4
00:01:58,743 --> 00:02:00,203
idem da pronadjem prijatelja.

5
00:02:00,245 --> 00:02:01,913
ako se ne vratim, onda znas
gde da posaljes moje stvari.

6
00:02:02,163 --> 00:02:03,331
Pa, sacekajte...

7
00:02:03,957 --> 00:02:05,417
Gospodine, sacekajte!

8
00:02:05,458 --> 00:02:06,459
Tolkien, gospodine!

9
00:02:06,918 --> 00:02:08,753
Gospodine, molim vas ne radite ovo.
Vi morate da se odmorite.

10
00:02:08,795 --> 00:02:10,088
Ne, dobro sam.

11
00:02:10,380 --> 00:02:12,841
Vrati se u baraci
i sacekaj me tamo.

12
00:02:12,882 --> 00:02:14,426
Gospodine, stvarno morate leci.

13
00:02:14,718 --> 00:02:17,053
- Ja stvarno ne mislim...
- Slusaj, Hodges, ostani ovde.

14
00:02:17,095 --> 00:02:19,848
To je naredjenje.

15
00:02:21,725 --> 00:02:24,019
Prekrijte lice, gospodine!
Ne dižite se!

16
00:02:34,612 --> 00:02:36,156
Ona voda je bila hladna.

17
00:02:38,074 --> 00:02:39,743
Treba da se ugrejete, gospodine.

18
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,746
Dugacko je putovanje do fronta.

19
00:02:46,875 --> 00:02:49,878
Ne verujem da ce nas noc
dobro tretirati, gospodine.

20
00:02:59,554 --> 00:03:03,099
Mlin Sarehole, Engleska

21
00:03:07,896 --> 00:03:10,231
Borite se, ljudi!
-Ima ih previse!

22
00:03:10,982 --> 00:03:12,817
Potrebno nam je pojacanje!

23
00:03:12,859 --> 00:03:13,818
Uzmi zastavu!

24
00:03:16,738 --> 00:03:18,365
Uzmi zastavu!

25
00:03:19,115 --> 00:03:21,493
Zaustavite ih!
On bezi!

26
00:03:30,543 --> 00:03:31,961
Gde je Tolkien?

27
00:03:33,421 --> 00:03:35,215
Gde je on?
-Tolkien!

28
00:03:48,812 --> 00:03:52,357
Molio sam se za jaku mazgu
koja ce mi pomoci da nosim kutije, i pogledaj,

29
00:03:52,399 --> 00:03:53,566
molitve su mi uslišene.

30
00:03:56,945 --> 00:03:57,987
Gde idemo?

31
00:03:58,029 --> 00:03:59,906
Birminghan. Idi do svoje sobe
I spakuj stvari.

32
00:03:59,948 --> 00:04:02,242
- Sta? Zasto?
- Zato sto sam rekla tako.

33
00:04:02,283 --> 00:04:04,202
Zato sto nam je otac Francis
pronasao novi smestaj.

34
00:04:04,244 --> 00:04:06,121
Vrlo je velikodušan.

35
00:04:06,162 --> 00:04:07,622
Nadji kutiju i skupi svoje stvari.

36
00:04:07,872 --> 00:04:08,957
Ne želim da idem u Birmingham.

37
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,042
Slušajte, obojica.

38
00:04:12,711 --> 00:04:13,795
Mi...

39
00:04:22,762 --> 00:04:24,055
Dodi ovamo, Hilary.

40
00:04:28,601 --> 00:04:31,604
Momci, pred nama su teska vremena,

41
00:04:31,646 --> 00:04:34,566
i imamo srece što nas Crkva podržava.

42
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,776
Od kad je vas otac preminuo...

43
00:04:36,818 --> 00:04:37,736
Ronalde.

44
00:04:49,706 --> 00:04:50,665
Ronalde!

45
00:05:05,263 --> 00:05:08,308
<i>Ubi bene ibi patria.</i>
</i>Secaš se toga, moja duso?

46
00:05:11,394 --> 00:05:14,647
Gde god se osecao srecan, tu je tvoj dom.

47
00:05:15,398 --> 00:05:17,817
<i>Naci cemo nase mesto, duso, naci cemo.</i>

48
00:05:20,153 --> 00:05:22,113
<i>Zakljucaj sve ovo u svom srcu.</i>

49
00:05:22,697 --> 00:05:25,575
<i>Zakljucaj cvrsto, i bice tu zauvek, ja ti obecavam.</i>

50
00:05:38,004 --> 00:05:40,423
<i>Momci, slušajte me.</i>

51
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:45,637
<i>Da li znate sta su siromašne okolnosti?</i>

52
00:05:47,389 --> 00:05:48,473
<i>Ono u cemu smo mi?</i>

53
00:05:48,515 --> 00:05:52,143
Dok sam bila devojcica,
svi novi romani pocinjali su ovako.

54
00:05:52,644 --> 00:05:55,480
Porodica dobrih i hrabrih ljudi

55
00:05:55,522 --> 00:05:58,775
Koja se nasla u iznenadnim siromasnim okolnostima.

56
00:05:59,442 --> 00:06:01,194
Kako su pobegli?

57
00:06:01,236 --> 00:06:04,239
Tako sto su nasli neko divno blago.

58
00:06:04,739 --> 00:06:06,324
Ili ako su se ozenili dobro.

59
00:06:07,117 --> 00:06:08,368
Ja se ne zenim ni sa kim.

60
00:06:08,910 --> 00:06:11,371
Znaci, morace da bude blago, zar ne?

61
00:06:11,413 --> 00:06:14,708
Ali, um, ljudi ne pronalaze blago, Majko.
Ne u stvarnom zivotu.

62
00:06:15,208 --> 00:06:18,003
Tebe je nemoguce prevariti,
zar ne, Jon Ronald?

63
00:06:20,505 --> 00:06:22,924
Recimo da postoji blago...

64
00:06:22,966 --> 00:06:24,551
i da postoji blago.

65
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:27,512
i neka tako ostane.

66
00:06:36,604 --> 00:06:38,356
Hajde da pocnemo, Ronald.

67
00:06:46,239 --> 00:06:50,577
Zemlja se zatresla od težine zmaja

68
00:06:50,618 --> 00:06:53,371
Kako je gmizao do vode,

69
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:56,583
a oblak otrova razleti se pred njim

70
00:06:56,624 --> 00:06:59,336
dok je frktao i urlikao!

71
00:07:00,003 --> 00:07:04,090
Ali Sigurd je cekao dok je zmaj 
dopuzeo preko jame,

72
00:07:05,425 --> 00:07:08,136
a onda mu je zario mac pod levo rame

73
00:07:08,178 --> 00:07:10,096
i pravo u njegovo srce.

74
00:07:10,764 --> 00:07:14,059
Zmaj je poceo lamatati repom
sve dok se kamenje nije razbilo,

75
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:16,311
I drvece srusilo oko njega.

76
00:07:17,771 --> 00:07:20,106
A onda je rekao, dok je umirao,

77
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:25,820
I rekao je, "Ko god bio ti koji me je porazio,

78
00:07:27,113 --> 00:07:32,202
Ovo zlato ce biti tvoja propast,
I propast svih koje ga zele."

79
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:34,120
Sigurd rece:

80
00:07:34,829 --> 00:07:36,289
"Ne bih ga ni taknuo,

81
00:07:36,331 --> 00:07:39,084
cak i ako ga izgubim,
Ja nikad necu umreti.

82
00:07:39,417 --> 00:07:40,877
Ali svi ljudi umiru,

83
00:07:40,919 --> 00:07:45,298
i nijedan hrabar covek ne dopusta smrcu
da ga zaplasi od svojih zelja."

84
00:07:49,094 --> 00:07:51,221
Znaš li kako apsurdno zvuciš?

85
00:07:51,262 --> 00:07:53,765
Stvarno? Još sam smešniji na latinskom.

86
00:07:56,017 --> 00:07:59,104
Znaš li šta to znaci?
Beznacajna bradavica.

87
00:07:59,145 --> 00:08:00,230
Ne.

88
00:08:00,271 --> 00:08:04,693
Smatram da sada zvuciš
kao pijani paun, blesane.

89
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:09,322
Zdravo, majko. Da li si mi donela marke?
-Zdravo, majko.

90
00:08:12,367 --> 00:08:13,993
Gde si ih stavila?

91
00:08:43,023 --> 00:08:43,898
Gospodine?

92
00:08:44,941 --> 00:08:46,776
Moram da nastavim
Dalje.

93
00:08:56,536 --> 00:08:58,455
Plin! Gospodine, plin.

94
00:09:33,239 --> 00:09:35,241
Zainteresovan sam da vidim momke.

95
00:09:42,874 --> 00:09:44,626
Pa, momci, bio sam upravu.

96
00:09:48,088 --> 00:09:51,299
Ona je ogromno stvorenje,
sa velikim ljuskavim stopalima

97
00:09:51,341 --> 00:09:54,469
i najistaknutijim
par kljova koje sam ikada video.

98
00:09:54,803 --> 00:09:58,515
Ona zvace, nešto što mi izgleda
kao butna kost mladog decaka.

99
00:10:03,353 --> 00:10:05,480
S druge strane, ima torte.

100
00:10:09,526 --> 00:10:12,487
King Edward's?
To je vrlo dobra škola.

101
00:10:12,779 --> 00:10:15,156
Pa, to su vrlo bistri momci,
gospodjo Faulkner.

102
00:10:15,532 --> 00:10:16,700
Vrlo vredni.

103
00:10:17,033 --> 00:10:19,202
Nakon Afrike,
majka ih je odgajala kod kuce

104
00:10:19,244 --> 00:10:21,204
i sad tecno govore mnogo jezika.

105
00:10:21,246 --> 00:10:23,123
Da, ali mislim drustveno.

106
00:10:23,915 --> 00:10:28,128
Momci, mešacete se s 
uglednom porodicom Birminghama.

107
00:10:28,628 --> 00:10:31,297
To je velika promena od 
Afrike , pretpostavljam.

108
00:10:31,673 --> 00:10:33,508
Oni žive u Engleskoj

109
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:35,719
daleko dalje
nego što su bili u Bloemfonteinu.

110
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:36,678
Nije li tako, momci?

111
00:10:37,262 --> 00:10:39,222
Da, jedva da više i nosimo koplja.

112
00:10:43,685 --> 00:10:45,562
Bilo je tesko da se smeste, zar ne?

113
00:10:45,603 --> 00:10:48,064
Imali su jedan ili dva privremena doma.

114
00:10:48,565 --> 00:10:52,235
Ono što im treba je, naravno,
civilizacijski uticaj

115
00:10:52,277 --> 00:10:55,280
stabilnog i preuradjenog okruženja.

116
00:10:55,321 --> 00:10:56,364
Poput vašega, gdo Faulkner.

117
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:58,283
Ako imam manu,

118
00:10:58,324 --> 00:11:01,995
to je prevelika velikodušnost
prema mojim mladim stanarima.

119
00:11:02,037 --> 00:11:03,329
Prevelika privrženost.

120
00:11:03,913 --> 00:11:08,752
Edith, jos jedno siroce,
doživljavam kao vlastito dete.

121
00:12:18,571 --> 00:12:19,906
Ustani, novi mladicu.

122
00:12:21,783 --> 00:12:23,535
<i>Tolkajn.</i>

123
00:12:26,204 --> 00:12:28,123
Kaže se <i>kin, </i>gospodine.

124
00:12:35,088 --> 00:12:37,632
Šta?
-Izgovara se <i>Tolkin, </i>gospodine.

125
00:12:37,674 --> 00:12:40,135
Ne <i>Tolkajn.
</i>Izvinite.

126
00:12:42,429 --> 00:12:43,638
Sedi.

127
00:12:48,518 --> 00:12:53,356
Kad smo vec od jutros
tako osetljivi na izgovaranje,

128
00:12:53,398 --> 00:12:56,568
Mozda bi bilo dobro da
izvaditi primerke Chaucera.

129
00:12:57,694 --> 00:13:01,656
Gospodin Tol-Keen moze da prati
najbolje sto moze.

130
00:13:02,824 --> 00:13:03,908
Mackintoshe. Pocnite.

131
00:13:11,833 --> 00:13:13,460
Oh, za ime gospoda.
Goodson-Thomase.

132
00:13:17,756 --> 00:13:19,007
Wisemane.

133
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,852
Gospodin. Tol-Keen.

134
00:14:17,899 --> 00:14:19,275
Dodaj Tolkienu.
Van, široko!

135
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:31,621
Budalo!

136
00:14:37,877 --> 00:14:40,588
Ne pricaj.
Da ni rec nisi rekao.

137
00:14:41,047 --> 00:14:42,799
Šta ako me nešto pita?

138
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,000
Nece.

139
00:14:44,968 --> 00:14:46,886
Ne zanimaš ga ti.

140
00:14:47,929 --> 00:14:49,097
Udjite.

141
00:14:58,857 --> 00:15:01,359
Zar mislite da nemam pametnijeg posla

142
00:15:01,401 --> 00:15:03,236
Nego da resavam vase svadje?

143
00:15:03,278 --> 00:15:05,113
Ne, gospodine.
Apsolutno ne.

144
00:15:05,488 --> 00:15:08,867
Odnosi na koledžu
su temelj ucenja.

145
00:15:08,908 --> 00:15:10,785
Zar ne kažemo tako u King Edward'su?

146
00:15:11,244 --> 00:15:14,456
Direktore, s postovanjem,,
Gilson i ja smo samo igrali ragbi.

147
00:15:14,998 --> 00:15:17,625
Pomalo nasilno, priznajem, ali...

148
00:15:29,220 --> 00:15:32,015
Muskarci bi tebalo biti drugovi.
Odakle god da poticu.

149
00:15:32,891 --> 00:15:34,059
Od najvišeg

150
00:15:34,642 --> 00:15:36,311
do najnižeg.

151
00:15:37,645 --> 00:15:40,523
Vi i Gospodin...
-Tolkien.

152
00:15:40,565 --> 00:15:42,859
...demonstriracete ostatku skole.

153
00:15:43,651 --> 00:15:46,863
Sve cete raditi zajedno
do kraja polugodišta.

154
00:15:46,905 --> 00:15:48,656
Ali, gospodine...
-Sve.

155
00:15:51,034 --> 00:15:52,035
Da, gospodine.

156
00:15:52,827 --> 00:15:55,455
Pretvorio nas je u vazale.
-Nije li to preterano?

157
00:15:55,497 --> 00:15:58,416
To je nemoguci standard.
Smišljen je da me ponizi.

158
00:15:58,458 --> 00:16:01,127
Ne ponižava li i mene?
-Ti si nebitan.

159
00:16:01,169 --> 00:16:03,046
Zašto stalno to govoriš?
-Jer je istina.

160
00:16:03,088 --> 00:16:05,006
Ne, slušaj.
Mozda ne dolazim iz ugledne okoline

161
00:16:05,048 --> 00:16:07,258
Ne zato, idiote.
Nebitan si direktoru.

162
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:09,010
A ti nisi?
-Ne.

163
00:16:09,260 --> 00:16:11,096
Jer si poseban.

164
00:16:12,138 --> 00:16:13,390
Jer sam njegov sin.

165
00:17:24,878 --> 00:17:26,504
Molim te, ne prestaj, Edith.

166
00:17:42,145 --> 00:17:43,605
Christophere, dragi.
-Gilsone.

167
00:17:43,646 --> 00:17:45,648
Christophere, budi miran.

168
00:17:45,690 --> 00:17:47,984
Gilsone, ne budi smešan.
-Christophere. Sedni.

169
00:17:48,026 --> 00:17:49,611
Stani!
-Chrise, sedni.

170
00:17:49,652 --> 00:17:51,196
U bilbioteci smo.
Christopher, sedi dole.

171
00:17:51,237 --> 00:17:52,530
Šta?

172
00:18:05,418 --> 00:18:07,504
Idemo na caj.

173
00:18:07,545 --> 00:18:09,255
Pa?
-Pa...

174
00:18:09,297 --> 00:18:11,174
Pretpotstavljam da 
treba da radimo sve zajedno...

175
00:18:11,216 --> 00:18:12,676
Ostacu ovde, hvala ti.

176
00:18:12,717 --> 00:18:13,885
Kako god zelis.

177
00:18:24,604 --> 00:18:26,231
Nije zeleo da dodje.

178
00:18:36,533 --> 00:18:38,660
Robert je zeleo da kaze

179
00:18:38,702 --> 00:18:42,455
da je, uz malo ohrabrenja od prijatelja,

180
00:18:42,956 --> 00:18:46,292
sada priznao da je za ovu kaznu
kriv on sam, a ne ti,

181
00:18:47,002 --> 00:18:49,421
I voleo bi da se iskupi,
Tako sto te poziva na caj.

182
00:18:50,588 --> 00:18:52,424
Trebao bi biti polaskan, stvarno.

183
00:18:52,465 --> 00:18:54,676
Tvoja ga je domišljatost uzrujala.

184
00:18:55,593 --> 00:18:58,680
Uzrujala bi i tebe,
kad bi imao oca poput Gilsonovog.

185
00:18:58,972 --> 00:19:02,350
Ocene mu samo trebaju pasti
ispod jednog ucenika godišnje...

186
00:19:02,851 --> 00:19:04,936
To nije izgovor, ali...

187
00:19:07,188 --> 00:19:08,648
Dodji.

188
00:19:08,690 --> 00:19:11,234
Daleko je zabavnije
od sedenja uz hrpu starih knjiga.

189
00:19:11,276 --> 00:19:12,694
Volim knjige.

190
00:19:13,153 --> 00:19:14,654
Kao i mi.

191
00:19:17,532 --> 00:19:19,451
Geoffrey Bache Smith.

192
00:19:20,535 --> 00:19:22,495
John Ronald Reuel Tolkien.

193
00:19:23,496 --> 00:19:25,707
Gospodo. Pomisao.
-Tolkiene.

194
00:19:25,749 --> 00:19:27,125
Zamislite da udjete u <i>Barrow's</i>

195
00:19:27,167 --> 00:19:29,586
i zateknete mene kako cuvam vrata
s vrlo velikim štapom...

196
00:19:29,627 --> 00:19:30,795
Gde ovo vodi?

197
00:19:30,837 --> 00:19:33,340
I kažem: "Tu nema potrebe
jesti tortu. Vec jesam.

198
00:19:33,381 --> 00:19:35,091
Zapravo, toliko da mi se smucilo."

199
00:19:35,383 --> 00:19:37,385
To je narav roditeljskog autoriteta.

200
00:19:37,427 --> 00:19:39,346
"Ja sam to ucinio.
Zakljucio sam da je loše.

201
00:19:39,387 --> 00:19:41,014
Sad cu tebi onemoguciti da to uciniš."

202
00:19:41,056 --> 00:19:43,183
S tim da su torte u primeru...
-Sve.

203
00:19:43,224 --> 00:19:44,267
Sve što je dobro.
-Tacno.

204
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:47,103
Tolkiene, ovo je <i>Barrow's.</i>

205
00:19:47,145 --> 00:19:49,939
Naše kraljevstvo, i najbolji caj u gradu.

206
00:20:01,701 --> 00:20:03,411
Još jedan cajnik?
-Hvala vam.

207
00:20:03,453 --> 00:20:06,081
A šta imate jeftinije od šilinga?
-A da nije tost.

208
00:20:06,122 --> 00:20:08,667
Peciva iz Batha za cetiri penija.
-Dobro. Pecivo iz Batha, molim.

209
00:20:08,708 --> 00:20:10,627
I tri viljuske.
-Cetiri.

210
00:20:10,669 --> 00:20:12,837
A što cemo sa štapom?
-Štapom?

211
00:20:12,879 --> 00:20:14,589
Moj otac je savršen primer.

212
00:20:14,631 --> 00:20:16,341
Razume se u muziku.
Voli je.

213
00:20:16,383 --> 00:20:19,260
Veci deo svoje mladosti
je izucavao i komponovao muziku.

214
00:20:19,302 --> 00:20:21,888
Christopheru su objavili
nekoliko muzickih dela.

215
00:20:21,930 --> 00:20:23,181
Ne nekoliko. Jedno.

216
00:20:23,223 --> 00:20:24,265
Dodaj mi šecer.

217
00:20:24,307 --> 00:20:27,060
A ipak, kad je rec
o životnom pozivu kompozitora?

218
